    <item>
      <title>巴西政局：卢拉批准削减开支，支持财政规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/brazil-politics-lula-approves-spending-cuts-backs-fiscal-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 宣布，政府将削减 259 亿雷亚尔（47 亿美元）的强制性支出，并表示总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦已批准此举，并且将尊重国家的财政框架。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/brazil-politics-lula-approves-spending-cuts-backs-fiscal-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉削减开支带来暂时缓解，巴西资产上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/brazil-assets-rally-as-lula-spending-cuts-bring-temporary-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 宣布削减开支以帮助实现国家财政目标，为市场带来了喘息机会，随后巴西资产周四再次全面上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/brazil-assets-rally-as-lula-spending-cuts-bring-temporary-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
